by <a href="/wiki/C._J._Cherryh" title="C. J. Cherryh">C. J. Cherryh</a></b></td>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b><a href="/wiki/Hugo_Award_for_Best_Novel" title="Hugo Award for Best Novel">Hugo Award for Best Novel</a></b><br />
<a href="/wiki/1990_in_literature" title="1990 in literature">1990</a></td>
